Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drink so much just because you couldn't get any customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.21,0:00:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always the one who has to come and get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.46,0:00:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do appreciate... that I have a good little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.72,0:00:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.83,0:00:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.29,0:00:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.87,0:01:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this where Judy Devens died?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all called you Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.80,0:01:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know who that is. Judy told me he goes around the country killing gangsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.39,0:01:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a real assassin then?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.90,0:01:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom, the assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:02:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... you are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please kill them all. You can have this money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who came to that alley last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.96,0:02:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who fired a gun there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who was supposed to receive this money...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please kill every single one who was involved in Judy's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judy... I was able to get acquainted with Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that Reiji will avenge your death...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for that five million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:02:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you straight. Five million isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the shortfall is small enough... that you can earn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.68,0:03:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be my assistant for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.36,0:03:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming your assistant means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I can be by your side when you avenge Judy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, there's something we have to pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you pick the one you want the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want all the clothes here equally.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I pick one, that means I have to give up everything else, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. This isn't the only opportunity for you to shop in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's something you want, I'll bring you here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. So today, you can pick the one you wanna wear now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, do I look cute? Do I look good in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You look really good in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never worn such light, smooth clothes before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.32,0:04:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a bit, okay? I'll prepare food when I'm done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you cleaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's really dirty in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An assassin who cleans his room...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't seem like much of an assassin, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can leave this kind of stuff to me, your assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be useful to you in order to earn what that five million doesn't cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Reiji... Do you have a family?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are your parents already...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I ran away from the worst damn excuse of a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Judy took me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.17,0:05:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it wasn't for her, I'd have been dead by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you two are sisters, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. She's the only family I got.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Judy is dead now and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Judy's dead, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should I go? What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know... what to do, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People die in different ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:06:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal, give me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your compensation for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take good care of it... always.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The main actors have all gathered now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Claudia, who cunningly used me and is once again devising a plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daisuke Godo, who plans to encroach upon Inferno with her help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wisemel, who noticed that plot and is now trying to stop it by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in addition, a new actor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall make this play the best one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:07:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we will be busy from here on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that he's Judy's killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least he's one of those who were responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.63,0:08:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is! There's someone behind the water tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,0:09:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.18,0:09:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Mr. Godo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That surprised me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W... wanted to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you shot?! Did it hit you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do such a reckless thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see his face at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did a good job, observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was Judy's killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You avenged her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Leave immediately via route C and await your next instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I heard a rumor... that Isaac of the Bloodies died. Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's over... the revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Uhm... How was my training to become an assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you like, shall I continue to help you with your assassinations?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about being a killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:12:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Then I'm no longer needed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd hate to give up that cooking of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can be my maid and do the cooking for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! All right! I'm gonna be a maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to try being a maid once. The uniform is really cute, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.43,0:12:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still want to become your assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.65,0:12:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know... that you don't want me to become an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the pain that comes with being an assassin, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal, you can take any path. You can become anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all things, why do you want to become an assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like assassins?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you don't like yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I don't. I ended up becoming a killer and can't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already broken. Do you want to be like me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm sorry, Reiji... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:14:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal... I was too harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true. I don't know how many people have died because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They would've been able to live on if it wasn't for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They would've been able to go back to their loved ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just doing the job that someone has to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then did you want to kill people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you shoot those people because you wanted to kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like killing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once you kill, everything in the world changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The scenery you see, the sounds you hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:15:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to accept people with a kind heart like you're able to right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to become like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a good place for you to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't come into the same world I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's where you're always gonna be, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I go there, I'll be able to be with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be separated from you. I want to be with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be of help to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.74,0:15:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could be with you if I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. I'll go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come to your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll go. Let me go back... to the world you live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.11,0:16:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji... You said you'd be by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.35,0:16:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised... You promise, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you have to work this late...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not come home until late. So go ahead and go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll stay up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a broken VCR this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see if I can fix it, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can buy a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be a waste. It might still work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might still work... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It works!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.40,0:17:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the video rental store is still open...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}In this case, the Peace Party will have to stop their support to the Middle East.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Then, from the viewpoint of international support, it'll provoke antipathy from...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji! Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go in! It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Reiji is...! Reiji is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.93,0:18:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.28,0:18:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be back, right? You promised, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said we'd never be separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you'd stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. He's a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been deceiving you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who... are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to cry at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go back to being your old self now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
